"Dear Hiring Manager, This letter serves as an opportunity to get to know more about me as a prospective challenge for the position of Junior Software Engineer as advertised on Acroquest Myanmar Technology Co., Ltd. Official LinkedIn Page. I would like to tell you about my skills. background and ability to succeed in the position. My interest in the position stems from a desire to use diverse programming skills towards solving technological challenges. My training as an Software Engineer, along with the ability to OOP Concepts, Strong knowledge of Java, Storing procedures like SQLite database and REST API make me an ideal candidate for this position. I know that I would be a valuable asset to your team at Acroquest Myanmar Technology Co., Ltd Company. I am eager to take on a new challenge and I see this as the perfect opportunity to contribute and grow for me. I am excited to be applying for this position. In my resume, you can find more information on the skills and personal projects. I'd be happy to provide greater detail about my skills and experience during an interview. Please call me at your earliest convenience. Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you.
